# Project Structure & Patterns

## Architecture Overview
- **Backend**: Laravel API in `/api/`
- **Frontend**: React (Material-UI v7) in `/web/`
- **Setup**: Docker-based with services defined in [docker-compose.yml](mdc:docker-compose.yml)

## Key Files & Directories
- **API Routes**: [api/routes/api.php](mdc:api/routes/api.php)
- **React Pages**: `web/src/pages/`
- **React Components**: `web/src/components/`
- **API Services**: [web/src/services/api.ts](mdc:web/src/services/api.ts)

## Critical Patterns

**Material-UI v7 Grid**:
```typescript
<Grid size={{ xs: 12, md: 6 }}>...</Grid>
```

**Safe Array Mapping**:
```typescript
{(items || []).map(item => ...)}
```

**API Response Handling**:
```typescript
// Always use a fallback to prevent errors
setData(response.data || response || []);
```